Good one, lad. You got him.

34:30.368 --> 34:31.668
(exhaling):
Oh...

34:31.670 --> 34:33.503
Why are you being so thoughtful?

34:33.505 --> 34:35.172
I sat beside my brother

34:35.174 --> 34:37.474
As he went through
a round of the cures.

34:37.476 --> 34:40.077
But on the good side,
he did say the dry heat

34:40.079 --> 34:41.745
From the oven gave
him some relief

34:41.747 --> 34:44.081
From the sores
all over his body.

34:44.083 --> 34:47.217
I only have sores in my mouth
and on my hands,

34:47.219 --> 34:49.219
So it's not very helpful.

34:53.224 --> 34:55.225
Catherine... We
are both veterans

34:55.227 --> 34:57.527
Of the game, are we not,
so I hope you'll forgive

34:57.529 --> 35:00.697
The question, but is it possible
that you don't have syphilis?

35:00.699 --> 35:02.766
That you've been poisoned?

35:02.768 --> 35:05.268
Don't you think
I take precautions?

35:05.270 --> 35:06.837
I meant no offense.

35:06.839 --> 35:09.106
But it does seem strange
that your sores

35:09.108 --> 35:10.607
Are exactly where you
would touch food,

35:10.609 --> 35:12.576
Picking it up, putting
it into your mouth?

35:12.578 --> 35:16.179
My system of food tasters
is impeccable.
Yes,

35:16.181 --> 35:18.181
But not all poison
is delivered through food.

35:18.183 --> 35:20.250
Is there something
that...

35:20.252 --> 35:24.254
(sighs) you touch often,
something no one else uses?

35:26.257 --> 35:28.859
Uh... Not your clothing--

35:28.861 --> 35:31.294
Your laundress cleanses that.

35:31.296 --> 35:32.696
Wait.

35:34.599 --> 35:37.200
I do read henry's bible.

35:37.202 --> 35:38.802
I took it from his room

35:38.804 --> 35:40.504
After his death--
I've been reading it

35:40.506 --> 35:42.472
For comfort
nearly every day.

35:42.474 --> 35:44.541
It belonged to henry,
and henry went mad.

35:44.543 --> 35:47.244
And now it belongs to you.

35:48.212 --> 35:50.714
This will tell us.

35:50.716 --> 35:52.415
(sighs)

35:53.684 --> 35:55.719
(sizzles)

35:55.721 --> 35:58.522
The book is deadly.

