Hold... My bottle.

36:39.398 --> 36:40.564
No.

36:40.566 --> 36:42.365
No.

36:42.367 --> 36:43.733
My sword. No.

36:43.735 --> 36:45.569
My... Bottle.

36:45.571 --> 36:47.237
(sighs):
Ah.

36:48.506 --> 36:50.340
(grunts)

36:50.342 --> 36:51.508
Oh, how I...

36:51.510 --> 36:53.376
Love...

