37:00.219 --> 37:01.918
By the way.
We will lie...

37:01.920 --> 37:04.721
In front...
Of the villa cortello

37:04.723 --> 37:06.489
On the beach,

37:06.491 --> 37:09.392
Drinking and making love
in the sand.

37:09.394 --> 37:11.228
Well, good luck--
the villa cortello's

37:11.230 --> 37:12.429
Miles from the ocean.

37:12.431 --> 37:14.431
I somehow doubt your
"beauties" will appreciate

37:14.433 --> 37:17.734
Climbing up and down
a cliff each day.

37:19.237 --> 37:21.605
Let's go inside.

37:29.947 --> 37:32.315
(door closes)

37:33.284 --> 37:34.784
I'm sorry.
I know I said

37:34.786 --> 37:36.753
I'd try to be back
for the feast.

37:36.755 --> 37:38.288
Did you even try?

37:38.290 --> 37:39.289
Or were you happier

37:39.291 --> 37:41.491
Being away from me right now?

37:42.260 --> 37:44.527
I wish
you believed

37:44.529 --> 37:45.629
How sorry I am.

37:45.631 --> 37:48.298
I'm sorry that I
got in so deep

37:48.300 --> 37:49.532
With henry,
that I thought

37:49.534 --> 37:51.268
Of only my own survival.

37:51.270 --> 37:52.802
Sorry because
now that I know

37:52.804 --> 37:54.571
Real love,
I've disappointed you.

37:54.573 --> 37:56.940
I believe that you're sorry.

37:56.942 --> 37:59.743
I wish you could look at me
like you once did.

37:59.745 --> 38:01.444
I'm still the
same person,

38:01.446 --> 38:03.446
The same woman you loved.

38:03.448 --> 38:06.349
Tonight I saw a man killed
in front of me

38:06.351 --> 38:08.385
Because people thought
he was a monster.

38:08.387 --> 38:09.619
They knew one thing about him,

38:09.621 --> 38:11.621
And that was dark enough
that in their minds

38:11.623 --> 38:14.391
They erased him
as a human being.
They didn't wait

38:14.393 --> 38:16.026
To see the truth of his heart.

38:16.028 --> 38:18.395
I'm not sure
what it is you're saying...

38:18.397 --> 38:20.897
Or that I really like you
using the word "monster"

38:20.899 --> 38:22.732
When we were
just talking about <i>me.</i>

38:22.734 --> 38:25.568
(sighs)
I don't want to make
the same mistakes

38:25.570 --> 38:27.370
As those people tonight.

38:27.372 --> 38:28.805
I don't want
to kill

38:28.807 --> 38:30.740
Something out of ignorance.

38:30.742 --> 38:33.743
So does that mean
you're willing to forgive me?

38:33.745 --> 38:36.479
I mean that I want to see
your heart, kenna,

38:36.481 --> 38:38.481
And not just one part of it,

38:38.483 --> 38:40.884
The entire truth of it,
no matter how dark.

38:40.886 --> 38:43.086
Because that's what marriage
is all about.

38:43.088 --> 38:46.423
It can take years
to see what's inside.
Years?

38:46.425 --> 38:48.425
Bash, my heart really
isn't that complicated.

38:48.427 --> 38:51.361
Trust me, your heart
is complicated.

38:51.363 --> 38:54.764
It's like one of those
drinks at christmas
with too much spice.

38:54.766 --> 38:57.600
Nutmeg and ginger
and cinnamon and cloves.

38:57.602 --> 38:59.069
But what can I say?

38:59.071 --> 39:01.104
I've developed
a taste for spice.

