What are you going to do?

39:26.365 --> 39:27.630
Justice says he should suffer

39:27.632 --> 39:28.832
The way marcus suffered.

39:28.834 --> 39:30.767
He'll ache for death

39:30.769 --> 39:34.671
Long before that gift
