39:37.509 --> 39:39.943
(bell tolling in distance)

39:39.945 --> 39:42.979
What can we possibly do

39:42.981 --> 39:45.482
Or say to convince elizabeth
that I'm not a threat?

39:45.484 --> 39:48.618
That I'm not seeking
to topple her?

39:49.553 --> 39:50.487
(sighs)

39:50.489 --> 39:52.956
There's nothing.

39:52.958 --> 39:55.825
For the rest of our lives,
she will distrust us.

39:55.827 --> 39:58.962
We can't explain
my actions to her
or anybody,

39:58.964 --> 40:01.464
Because every explanation
leads back to...

40:01.466 --> 40:02.532
The blackmail,

40:02.534 --> 40:04.000
The secret...

